measurements.description:
Eighty-four flowers and 48 buds on 14 up to 3.1 cm inflorescences;
 16-cm wide by 14-cm tall leafless plant growing on six-cm x ten-cm compressed cork;
 stellate flowers translucent white;
 sepals lanceolate, light green vein centrally;
 petals ovate, slightly porrect;
 lip flat, widely ovate, spur seven mm long;
 column white, anther cap yellow;
 substance light; texture crystalline; also awarded AM #20255289.
